   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In 2015, 219 legal medical evaluations were carried out for alleged sexual offenses in the municipality of Bello, which places it second in number of cases after Medellin and as one of the highest in the country. To prevent the occurrence of new cases, The Dar Luz Foundation, together with the authorities of the municipality, will execute a training program aimed at training students, parents, teachers and leaders to prevent and deal with the occurrence of acts of sexual abuse</narrative>
